lead_paragraph: Aaron Wise rebounded from an unpromising start with an ace and eagle in consecutive holes to surge into contention for the OHL Classic at Mayakoba on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Golf: Wise Soars High With Ace-eagle Run in Mexico
